elements.name: To verify that modification message is sent to Subscriber successfully.

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin User
Navigate to User Management and Click on manage user
enter user mobile number and search the user
System Admin is able to view details
System Admin is able to edit KYC details
Confirm the edit details
Logout
Login into Mobiquity Portal as another System admin User after Logout
Navigate to Approvals and filter by Submitted status
User click on submitted user data
verify message sent to user

elements.name: To verify that the System Admin is able to suspend a subscriber successfully through web.

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin User
Navigate to User Management and Click on manage user
enter user mobile number and search the SuspendResume user
System Admin is able to view details
Suspend the user by giving the comment
Verify the user suspend Confirmation message
Logout
Login into Mobiquity Portal as another System admin User after Logout
Navigate to Approvals
Admin click on Suspended user data
Approve to suspended the Users
Verify the user Suspended approval message

elements.name: To verify that the System Admin is able to resume a suspend subscriber successfully through web.

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin User
Navigate to User Management and Click on manage user
enter user mobile number and search the SuspendResume user
Resume the user by giving the comment
Verify the user resume Confirmation message
Logout
Login into Mobiquity Portal as another System admin User after Logout
Navigate to Approvals
Admin click on Resumeded user data
Approve the Resumed User
Verify the user Resumed approval message
